 scientist fails from the field when studying animals goes wrong Babysitter abused girl and got away with it after calling her 'touchy feely' Man arrested for allegedly displaying banned Hong Kong 'liberation' slogan Hundreds rally behind mother whose son died after being restrained for eating a biscuit NSW Attorney General calls for answers on harassment in legal system, launching 'robust' review Woman assaulted near Torture Hill track in Adelaide conservation park Most Popular 1. Melbourne's 3031 postcode is in the top four for COVID-19 cases this week, but isn't a 'hotspot' 2. Ghislaine Maxwell was hiding out in a secluded $US1 million hilltop home. Then the FBI came knocking 3. Health authorities investigating Melbourne 'super spreader' theory 4. Babysitter abused girl and got away with it after calling her 'touchy feely' 5. Hundreds rally behind mother whose son died after being restrained for eating a biscuit 6. Heavily armed SA Police unit prompts backlash and 'gun culture' concern Top Stories Melbourne's 3031 postcode is in the top four for COVID-19 cases this week, but isn't a 'hotspot' Federal health authorities say it's too early to know if coronavirus cases are stabilising in Victoria Health authorities investigating Melbourne 'super spreader' theory Man from coronavirus hotspot arrives in Sydney on train as locals queue for tests after Woolworths scare Ghislaine Maxwell was hiding out in a secluded $US1 million hilltop home. Then the FBI came knocking Who is Ghislaine Maxwell? How does she link Jeffrey Epstein to Prince Andrew? Sivo claims four-try haul in Eels' thrashing of Cowboys as Raiders stave off Dragons Heavily armed SA Police unit prompts backlash and 'gun culture' concern Concerns over coronavirus hospitalisation trend Just In Reds break seven-year drought against Waratahs to launch Super Rugby AU Posted  21 m minutes ago Fri Friday  3  Jul July  2020 at 12:27pm Sivo claims four-try haul in Eels' thrashing of Cowboys as Raiders stave off Drago